NHS employees and volunteers will also conduct mobile investigations with portable detectors.
In a noise analysis of all shots by experts, the frequency of bat exclamations is determined and which species does what.
Subsequently, a map and report of the habitat is created to create a detailed picture of their behavior at the landscape level.
